y rehydration; no API client codegen; do not change apps/api response shapes (web adapts).\n\n## Process requirements\n- **Commit your own work** with conventional commits (e.g. `feat(web): …`, `feat(api): …`). Do NOT ask the human to commit for you. Co-Authored-By trailer is fine.\n- **Self-test before you finish** and fix failures: `pnpm --filter web lint`, `pnpm --filter web build`, and if you touched apps/api: `pnpm --filter api lint && pnpm --filter api build && pnpm --filter api test`. If you changed apps/api auth/HTTP/schema/RLS, also run `apps/api/scripts/rls-test.sh` (normalize CRLF first if it complains: `sed -i 's/\\r$//' apps/api/scripts/rls-test.sh`).\n- If a step is genuinely ambiguous, prefer the spec's recommended default; do not expand scope.\n- Report a concise summary of what you changed and the test results when done.",
